org.eclipse.viatra.dse.objectives.impl

Class ModelQueriesGlobalConstraint

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.viatra.dse.objectives.impl.ModelQueriesGlobalConstraint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IGlobalConstraint

    public class ModelQueriesGlobalConstraint
extends java.lang.Object
implements IGlobalConstraint
    This global constraint collects a list of IncQuery pattern and checks if any of them has a match on along a trajectory. If any of the patterns has a match then it is unsatisfied and the exploration should backtrack.
    Author:
    Andras Szabolcs Nagy
